title: How many fingerprints can I save?
answer:
You can save up to 5 fingerprint templates under Settings > Fingerprint ID > Fingerprint management. 

 If you go to Settings > Security > Privacy protection and enable the privacy protection, you can create a fingerprint template for visitors. When you access the phone in visitor mode, you can save another 5 fingerprint templates under Settings > Fingerprint ID > Fingerprint management. To check all the fingerprint templates in both owner and visitor mode, go to Settings > Security > Privacy protection, enter the password, and select Manage fingerprints. 

 When a finger presses on the fingerprint sensor, its fingerprint template is highlighted in the template list.
